    "body": "Closes #10638.\r\nFixes #12235.\r\n\r\n- If the spack target is a generic (e.g. x86_64), OpenBLAS will now use\r\n  the 'DYNAMIC_ARCH' setting instead of targeting the host architecture\r\n- Translate spack-defined microarchitecture into OpenBLAS TARGET=\r\n  argument\r\n- Removes 'target', 'virtual_machine', 'avx2', 'avx512' variants as they\r\n  are no longer needed\r\n- Adds option to disable build of static libraries",
